N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 805.4 - Determination of the commissioner

State Regulations

The commissioner or his duly authorized representative
shall respond to the employee contest petition within 15 working days. The
commissioner's determination may grant, modify or deny a petition filed
pursuant to sections 805.2 and
805.3
